## 🔄 Version History

### v1.0 — Initial draft
**Date:** 31 March 2026 
**Prompt:** Document this background asset. Background: [PASTE DESCRIPTION HERE]
**Output:**  No props list, no continuity dependencies, no character interaction zones, no asset ID. 
**Observed effect:** Documentation unusable as a production record — all fields had to be manually created from scratch. Faster to document without AI.
**Lesson learned:**  Documentation prompts need a fixed field template to produce structured, production-ready output.

### v1.1 — Added fixed field template + asset ID format ✅ Current
**Date:** 31 March 2026 
**Change:** Added all required documentation fields, asset ID format, props included/excluded split, continuity dependencies field
**Output:** Correct field structure but no grounding constraint 
**Observed effect:** Fabricated props logged into production database — required manual audit and correction before compositing began
**Lesson learned:** Grounding constraint essential 

